I"÷<h3 id="1-carnation">1. Carnation</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Carnation often dedicated to mothers. It is the most representative flower of women. The most typical graduation flower is given to graduates who have completed a degree or who have received excellent grade.</li>
  <li>Red carnations symbolize admiration, worship, affection, warm love and longing for the mother and wish her a long and healthy life.</li>
  <li>White carnations express gratitude to mother, wish mother young and healthy, and express condolences and deep feelings of missing the late mother.</li>
  <li>Pink carnations symbolize the love of beauty and youth and hope that mothers will remain young and beautiful forever. In blessing mother birthday gift, wish mother forever beautiful young.
<img src="/images/mom01.jpg" alt="" />
<br /></li>
</ul>

